<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;border-top: 1px solid #C0C0C0;"><a href="/wiki/File:Portal.svg" class="image" title="Portal.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c9/Portal.svg/20px-Portal.svg.png" width="20" height="20" border="0" /></a> <a href="/wiki/Portal:Literature" title="Portal:Literature">Literature portal</a></th>
