t&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Rupert Rhymes (page does not exist)">Rupert Rhymes</a> (2002)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Sam_Mendes" title="Sam Mendes">Sam Mendes</a> (2003)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Judi_Dench" title="Judi Dench">Judi Dench</a> (2004)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Alan_Bennett" title="Alan Bennett">Alan Bennett</a> (2005)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Ian_McKellen" title="Ian McKellen">Ian McKellen</a> (2006)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/John_Tomlinson_(bass)" title="John Tomlinson (bass)">John Tomlinson</a> (2007)&#160;<b>·</b></span> <span style="white-space:nowrap"><a href="/wiki/Andrew_Lloyd_Webber" title="Andrew Lloyd Webber">Andrew Lloyd Webber</a> (2008)</span></p>
